Grace bahati  yavukiye  [[Uganda]]  tariki 15 werurwe 1991  we nu muryango we baje mu [[Rwanda]] afite imyaka 3 nyuma  ya [[Genocide mu Rwanda|genocide]] yakorewe abatutsi mu 1994 .yakutse mu muryango mugari . Bahati afite imyaka 16 yihaye intego yo gukora icyamuteza imbere.<ref>https://missrwanda.rw/grace-bahati/</ref>

== Miss Bahati Grace wa twaye ikamba 2009 ==
Miss Rwanda yabaye nyuma ya jenocide ,tariki 19 Ukuboza 2009 yegukanwa na Miss Bahati grace mubirori byabereye i Gikondo ahasanzwe habera  imurikagurisha.

yatwaye ikamba rya Miss Rwanda 2009 afite imyaka 18.<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/imyidagaduro/ibirori/article/reba-uburanga-bw-abakobwa-bahataniye-ikamba-rya-miss-rwanda-2009-amafoto</ref>
== Ubukwe bwa Miss Bahati Grace ==
Miss babati yakoranye ubukwe na Murekezi pascifque umuhungu wa Fatikaramu  wamamaye akina mwikipe ya Royan sports<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/imyidagaduro/ibirori/article/reba-uburanga-bw-abakobwa-bahataniye-ikamba-rya-miss-rwanda-2009-amafoto</ref>.

yakoze ubukwe tariki 19 Nzeri 2021 ,Muri Reta zunze ubumwe na America mu mujyi wa Cedra Rapids muri Reta ya Iowa,akaba arinaho bahuriye ubwambere bateretana.<ref>/imyidagaduro/ibirori/article/ubukwe-bwa-miss-bahati-grace-n-umuhungu-wa-fatikaramu-bwashyushye</ref>

== Amateka ==
Bahati n'umukobwa wavukiye muri [[Uganda]] Mu mwaka wa 1991 kuwa 15 werurwe. [[Nyampinga w'u Rwanda#cite%20note-3|Miss Bahati]] yagiye muri [[Amerika]] kuwa 22 [[Kamena]] 2011. [[Nyampinga w'u Rwanda#cite%20note-3|Bahati Grace]] yavuye mu [[Rwanda]] agiye kwiga muri [[Amerika]] ariko ngo agezeyo yasanze amafaranga yari afite atamurihira n’igihembwe kimwe, bituma abanza gushaka ibyangombwa byatuma yiga mu ishuri atishyura.<ref>https://hose.rw/miss-bahati-grace-yavuze-ku-buzima-bwo-kurera-umwana-wenyine-nyuma-yo-gutandukana-ka-k8/</ref>Guhera ubwo ntabwo yongeye kugaruka mu Rwanda kubera impamvu z’amasomo no gushaka ubuzima. Miss Bahati Grace akabaye yaramaze igihe arimurukondo na Murekezi Pacifique umuhungu wa Fatikaramu wamamaye akina mu ikipe ya Rayon Sports baza kwiyemeza kurushinga . Ubukwe bwabo bwabereye muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika. [[Nyampinga w'u Rwanda#cite%20note-3|Miss Elsa na Miss Meghane]] Barabutashye .<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/imyidagaduro/ibirori/article/ubukwe-bwa-miss-bahati-grace-n-umuhungu-wa-fatikaramu-bwashyushye</ref>

Mbereyaho [[Miss Bahati grace|Miss Bahati]]  yatangarije itangazamakuru ko yatwaye  inda agifite ikamba rya Miss Rwanda akaza kubyarana n’umuhanzi K8 Kavuyo waje no kumureka, Miss Bahati ntiyacitse intege akomeza kwirwanaho muri Amerika kugeza akundanye na Murekezi kugeza ubu niwe mutware we .<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/imyidagaduro/ibirori/article/ubukwe-bwa-miss-bahati-grace-n-umuhungu-wa-fatikaramu-bwashyushye</ref> Muri ibyo bihe kandi yari afite umwana w’uruhinja, agomba kwitaho wenyine kuko yari Atari kumwe na se.<ref>https://www.igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/miss-bahati-grace-ari-mu-rwanda</ref>Bwari ubuzima butoroshye kuko nta wundi muryango yari ahafite kandi atahamenyereye. bahati agira Ati “Kurera umwana uri umubyeyi umwe ni ikintu kitoroshye, mu gihugu cy’amahanga urimo uragerageza kumenyera ubuzima bushya n’indi mico utari usanzwe umenyereye ariko byose bituruka ku ntego nari mfite.<ref>https://hose.rw/miss-bahati-grace-yavuze-ku-buzima-bwo-kurera-umwana-wenyine-nyuma-yo-gutandukana-ka-k8/</ref>Bahati Grace yavuze ko yaje kubona umuryango wambereye nk’ababyeyi umufasha kurera umwana wemu gihe yari afite akazi abifatanya no kwiga. bahati grace  aragira Ati “Nabanye nawe ndamurera ndiga sinavuga ko imbaraga nyinshi zari kuri njye gusa , naje kugirirwa ubuntu n’Imana impa umuryango mugari mwiza n’ubwo ababyeyi banjye bari mu Rwanda Inama yanyegereje abo babyeyi.<ref>https://hose.rw/miss-bahati-grace-yavuze-ku-buzima-bwo-kurera-umwana-wenyine-nyuma-yo-gutandukana-ka-k8/</ref>

== Icyo Avuga mu Kwibuka kucuro 28 ==
Bahati Grace aragita ati : kucuro  28 Abanya Rwanda twibuka Genocide yakorewe abatutsi mu 1994 .<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/116240/kwibuka28-miss-bahati-grace-yunamiye-sebukwe-wishwe-muri-jenoside-116240.html</ref>Gwarazirikana kandi agaha icyubahiro sebukwe Rapheal Murekezi wamenyekanye nka Fatikaramu warumubyeyi , umukinnyi wumupira wamaguru wikipe ya ryon siporo aho nyuma yaje nokuba umutoza <ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/116240/kwibuka28-miss-bahati-grace-yunamiye-sebukwe-wishwe-muri-jenoside-116240.html</ref>

